snippet.textDisplay: Oh, I loved this one when I heard it in game. Quite a dark theme, you can imagine how Samus is feeling- knowing that she's fighting someone on her side, but also knowing that if she doesn't kill him, he will kill her instead. A hard choice, echoed wonderfully in this theme. It keeps a tempo just high enough to keep the battle pumping but melancholy and sad enough to speak more than words could.

snippet.textDisplay: Rundas was the best in that game. Sucks that he died, he was Noxus merged with Iceman and had a steroid boost of awesomeness. Plus that voice actor was badass too. Top it all off with a theme and unforgettable battle like this and you've got an incredible character. Rundas will be sorely missed.
